Business Information: Massage Envy provides massage, skin care and total body stretch services which are an integral part of total body wellness. Keep your body working, schedule an appointment today! Each location is an independently owned and operated franchise.

At Relax Therapeutic Massage, we believe that no two people are identical and therefore each massage should and must be tailored to the specific needs of the individual. Accordingly, our therapists have been trained in Sports massage, Stress reduction, Neuromuscular, Deep Tissue, Hot Stone, Aroma therapy & Reflexology
